{"id":232812031,"title":"新手請教(增肌相關","content":"各位巨巨、翹臀大家晚安。\n\n小弟我最近開始練健身(兩個多月)\n一開始大概\n體脂30骨骼39(健工量的但他不給帶走)\n開始練之後一個月量一次，最近兩個月如下圖。\nhttps://i.imgur.com/THd5KVi.jpg\n\n體脂是有下來可是骨骼肌增加很少，想請問一下這樣是正常的嗎？(過了新手福利期之類的)\n\n如果還想要增肌的話(目標50XD)\n是要增加訓練強度？\n還是要吃更多碳水？\n\n感謝各位前輩指導。\n\n附錄：\n\n1.飲食\n低碳，低脂，高蛋白，每日攝取熱量控制在2000以下(基代)，目前還是在繼續減脂。\n\n2.訓練\n一周六練，一次大概在一個半小時左右，除了腿跟核心一練以外其他部位都是一周兩次，沒做有氧(扁平足痛苦)。","excerpt":"各位巨巨、翹臀大家晚安。小弟我最近開始練健身（兩個多月），一開始大概，體脂30骨骼39（健工量的但他不給帶走），開始練之後一個月量一次，最近兩個月如下圖。體脂是有下來可是骨骼肌增加很少，想請問一下這樣","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"9b5213d6-4427-4a3c-b788-efa19493631c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-02T12:44:08.695Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-02T12:44:08.695Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["重訓","減脂","健身","增肌","健身房"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"健身","forumAlias":"fitness","school":"國立清華大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/THd5KVi.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"302f84c7-e2fe-4ec3-9a2b-94c8a267c8d0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/THd5KVil.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/THd5KVil.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/THd5KVil.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-02T12:44:08.695Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-02T12:44:08.695Z"},{"id":"302f84c7-e2fe-4ec3-9a2b-94c8a267c8d0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/THd5KVi.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/THd5KVi","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/THd5KVil.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-02T12:44:08.695Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-02T12:44:08.695Z"}],"postAvatar":""}